ns%20and%20facilitation%20for%20an%20eco-community%20in%20Thailand%2C%20my%20current%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20enjoyed%20a%20slew%20of%20flings%20and%20a%20few%20longer%20relationships.%20I've%20also%20learned%20dating%20lessons%2C%20including%20the%20following%20three.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22272d84c3-b35c-4cfc-9d80-089a1f4d2ff6%5C%22%3E1.%20Avoid%20premature%20attachment%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20met%20at%20a%20Buddhism%20course%20in%20Nepal.%20He%20had%20long%20curly%20hair%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20time.%20I%20chased%20him%20for%20two%20weeks%20until%20he%20gave%20in%2C%20fell%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20me%2C%20and%20welcomed%20me%20into%20his%20apartment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20then%20went%20about%20passionately%20ignoring%20one%20of%20Buddhism's%20core%20tenets%3A%20non-attachment.%20Attachment%2C%20the%20Buddha%20said%2C%20was%20the%20root%20of%20suffering.%20Testing%20his%20theory%2C%20we%20became%20fiercely%20attached%20to%20a%20future%20we%20quickly%20planned%20out%20%E2%80%94%20one%20replete%20with%20copious%20amounts%20of%20curly-haired%20children.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20months%2C%20our%20quest%20to%20do%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20the%20Buddha%20had%20taught%20brought%20us%20face-to-face%20with%20another%20core%20tenet%20of%20Buddhism%3A%20impermanence.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20argued%20our%20way%20through%20nine%20countries%20and%20eventually%20broke%20up%2C%20we%20ended%20the%20relationship%20with%20a%20hand-in-hand%20walk%20around%20the%20Buddhist%20stupa%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20neighborhood%20where%20we%20first%20met.%20It%20realized%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-3-different-attachment-styles-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremature%20attachment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20vision%20that%20doesn't%20yet%20have%20a%20strong%20foundation%20doesn't%20work.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%2011%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20lesson%20I've%20had%20to%20learn%20a%20few%20more%20times%20since.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20sitting%20with%20camel%20on%20Mount%20Sinai%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de744e83b8099cf9fca6d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20with%20a%20camel%20on%20Mount%20Sinai%2C%20has%20made%20friends%20while%20dating%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad.%3Cp%3ECait%20Charles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f799bb6-33d2-4899-a580-c1c9c1ca62b3%5C%22%3E2.%20Find%20friendships%20in%20failed%20relationships%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20was%20Moishe.%20Ah%2C%20Moishe%2C%20like%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%20when%20you%20fear%20not%20being%20able%20to%20breathe%20anymore.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20a%20new%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20was%20spreading%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%202020%2C%20and%20the%20pandemic%20had%20just%20been%20announced.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20met%20on%20Nomad%20Soulmates%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-celibacy-to-avoid-dating-apps-bumble-campaign-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20digital%20nomads%20under%20the%20most%20surreal%20of%20circumstances.%20All%20flights%20were%20being%20canceled%2C%20and%20the%20world%20was%20in%20panic.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20seemed%20to%20mirror%20each%20other%20perfectly.%20We%20were%20both%20longtime%20travelers%20and%20secular%20Jews%20from%20the%20US.%20Both%20of%20us%20wanted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-regret-not-having-kids-child-free-decision-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20partner%2C%20but%20not%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20near%20impossibility%20to%20find%20within%20our%20demographic.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20we%20were%20both%20obsessed%20with%