n%20fascinated%20by%20relationship%20psychology%2C%20he%20was%20skeptical.%20We%20also%20didn't%20share%20the%20same%20long-term%20goals%3B%20for%20example%2C%20he%20was%20set%20on%20staying%20in%20Florida%2C%20while%20I%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20full%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20year%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20make%20something%20work%20that%20was%20doomed%20to%20fail.%20Spoiler%20alert%3A%20It%20failed.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20if%20you%20enter%20a%20relationship%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20probably%20won't%20work%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20you're%20probably%20right.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20have%20no%20regrets.%20The%20experience%20taught%20me%20to%20prioritize%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20healthy%20relationship%20in%20the%20future%20over%20the%20impulse%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20less-than-ideal%20one%20in%20the%20present.%20Nowadays%2C%20I%20let%20go%20more%20gracefully%20early%20on%20when%20I%20see%20that%20a%20connection%20is%20unlikely%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%20from%20these%20nomadic%20love%20affairs%20has%20been%20that%20it%20just%20doesn't%20bode%20well%20for%20a%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20or%20for%20your%20heart%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20yourself%20by%20taking%20big%20steps%20and%20making%20big%20plans%20early%20on.%20When%20you're%20dating%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20temptation%20to%20do%20so%20is%20strong%2C%20and%20connecting%20at%20a%20speed%20that%20would%20seem%20crazy%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20world%26quot%3B%20is%20commonplace.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnections%20often%20feel%20more%20intense%2C%20too%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ebecause%20we%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-lifestyle-lessons-drawbacks-challenges-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edigital%20nomads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0exist%20within%20a%20bubble%20of%20transience%20and%20time%20limits.%20There'