strong%3Eyears%20flying%20around%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20world%20and%20exploring%20new%20countries%20every%20other%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20cabin%20crew%20member%20was%20the%20best%20time%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%2C%20now%2029%2C%20told%20me%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20enjoyed%20the%20work-life%20balance%20it%20afforded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20flight%20attendant%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Singapore%20Airlines%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d7e2b3289b805d1db3e681%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETan%20applied%20to%20be%20a%20flight%20attendant%20on%20Singapore%20Airlines%2010%20times.%3Cp%3ECherry%20Tan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20her%20fifth%20year%2C%20Tan%20was%20hungry%20for%20a%20change%20in%20her%20life.%20Flying%20began%20to%20feel%20mundane%2C%20and%20she%20was%20uncertain%20about%20the%20job%20stability%20and%20career%20progression%20of%20being%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20Duncan%20Hsu%2C%20now%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E36%2C%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20chef%20in%20a%20hotel%20and%20wanted%20to%20start%20his%20own%20business.%20Tan%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eopen%20a%20hawker%20stall%20together%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-hawker-center-food-michelin-photos-tips-cost-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekopitiam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20open-air%20coffee%20shop%20selling%20a%20variety%20of%20dishes%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20May%2C%20the%20couple%20invested%2030%2C000%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20around%20%2423%2C000%2C%20of%20their%20own%20money%20to%20open%20a%20stall