Pro%20Max%2C%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%2C%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20Max%2C%20and%20iPad%20and%20Mac%20with%20M1%20and%20later%2C%20with%20device%20and%20Siri%20language%20set%20to%20US%20English.%20Let%20us%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20features%20users%20will%20soon%20get%20to%20try%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWriting%20Tools%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI-powered%20Writing%20Tools%20will%20be%20available%20across%20different%20Apple%20apps%20such%20as%20Mail%2C%20Messages%2C%20Notes%20and%20more.%20These%20tools%20offer%20several%20features%20such%20as%20text%20summarisation%2C%20text%20generation%2C%20text%20refining%2C%20and%20more.%20Users%20can%20also%20ask%20the%20AI%20to%20make%20a%20message%20or%20an%20email%20longer%20using%20the%20AI.%20Further%2C%20users%20can%20also%20rewrite%20it%20into%20different%20styles%20by%20using%20manual%20prompts%20as%20well.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENotification%20summarisation%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnother%20interesting%20feature%20arriving%20with%20iOS%2018%20update%20is%20notification%20summarisation.%20This%20feature%20uses%20Apple%20Intelligence%20to%20cut%20the%20clutter%20from%20a%20large%20number%20of%20notifications%20in%20two%20ways.%20First%2C%20priority%20notifications%20are%20automatically%20assessed%20by%20the%20AI%20and%20are%C2%A0added%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20stack.%20These%20notifications%20will%20also%20be%20summarised%20so%20users%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20through%20the%20details.%C2%A0Second%2C%20the%20AI%C2%A0will%20understand%20the%20content%20of%20the%20notification%20and%20show%20only%20those%20which%20require%20immediate%20attention.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EClean%20Up%20in%20images%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Clean%20Up%20feature%20is%20essentially%20an%20object%20removal%20feature%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20remove%20unwanted%20objects%20or%20people%20from%20an%20image.%20These%20could%20be%20people%20obstructing%20the%20view%20of%20a%20famous%20monument%20or%20an%20unfitting%20object%20placed%20in%20the%20background%20of%20a%20memorable%20selfie.%20The%20AI%20can%20remove%20these%20automatically%2C%20or%20let%20the%20user%20highlight%20a%20particular%20object%20or%20person%20to%20remove%20them%20and%20fill%20in%20the%20background.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Search%20in%20Photos%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EApple%20Intelligence%20will%20allow%20users%20to%20search%20their%20Photos%20app%20and%20the%20images%20stored%20there%20with%20natural%20language%20queries.%20Users%20can%20ask%20about%20specific%20images%20using%20descriptive%20prompts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmail%20Summary%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20summarise%20long%20email%20threads%20to%20prioritise%20the%20most%20important%20features.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EImage%20Playground%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20will%20allow%20users%20to%20generate%20custom%20emojis%20or%20generate%20images%20using%20Apple%20Intelligence.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrivate%20Cloud%20Compute%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Private%20Cloud%20Compute%20run%20%E2%80%9Cstateless%20data%20processing%E2%80%9D%20where%20the%20user's%20device%20sends%20data%20to%20PCC%20for%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20user's%20inference%20request.%20Apple%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20user%20data%20remains%20on%20the%20server%20only%20till%20it%20is%20returned%20to%20the%20device%20and%20%E2%80%9Cno%20user%20data%20is%20retained%20in%20any%20form%20after%20the%20response%20is%20returned.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20set%20of%20features%20will%20be%20available%20in%20US%20English.%20Localised%20English%20languages%20will%20be%20added%20in%20December%2C%20and%20support%20for%20more%20languages%20such%20as%20Chinese%2C%20Spanish%2C%20French%2C%20and%20Japanese%20will%20be%20added%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAI%20Features%20That%20Will%20Be%20Available%20With%20Future%20Updates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20abovementioned%20features%20will%20be%20available%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20there%20are%20other%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20which%20will%20be%20available%20with%20future%20iOS%20updates.%20These%20include%20the%20ChatGPT-relates%20features%2C%20the%20Siri%20upgrade%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Genmoji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChatGPT%20Integration%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EChatGPT%2C%20the%20chatbot%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20will%20be%20integrated%20within%20Siri%20and%20the%20systemwide%20Writing%20Tools.%20It%20will%20also%20provide%20the%20image%20and%20document%20processing%20capabilities%20of%20various%20tools%20within%20the%20device.%20The%20most%20important%20use-case%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Siri%2C%20which%20will%20be%20able%20to%20access%20the%20chatbot%20with%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20user%2C%20and%20provide%20both%20web-related%20queries%20as%20well%20as%20answer%20to%20questions%20that%20require%20a%20deeper%20expertise.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmarter%20Siri%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESiri%2C%20the%20virtual%20assistant%20for%20Apple%20devices%2C%20is%20also%20getting%20a%20major%20upgrade.%20Apple%20has%20promised%20a%20new%20AI-powered%20conversational%20capability%20that%20will%20allow%20the%20AI%20tool%20to%20interact%20with%20users%20in%20natural%20language.%20Siri%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20more%20complex%20tasks%20as%20well%20as%20carry%20out%20tasks%20within%20various%20apps.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenmoji%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EApple%20Intelligence%20will%20also%20release%20Genjomi%2C%20a%20visual%20tool%20that%20will%20turn%20a%20rough%20sketch%20into%20a%20related%20image.%20Users%20can%20also%20upload%20their%20images%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20an%20artistic%20interpretation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisual%20Intelligence%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUsers%20can%20tap%20the%20Camera%20Control%20button%20to%20activate%20AI%20and%20find%20more%20information%20about%20images%20captured.%20They%20can%20also%20book%20a%20reservation%20or%20tickets%20to%20a%20location.%20It%20is%20a%20visual%20lookup%20tool%2C%20similar%20to%20Google%20Lens.%20Further%2C%20it%20will%20also%20be%20integrated%20with%20ChatGPT%20to%20offer%20enhanced%20computer%20vision%20processing.%20Apple%20says%20users%20can%20upload%20an%20image%20of%20a%20mathematical%20problem%20and%20find%20solutions%20to%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fq2uuPJt6lhU%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725911040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Fapple_intelligence_siri_1725894893773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fai%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-launch-apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-update-features-6527298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20the%20much-awaited%20integration%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20features%20into%20Apple%20devices%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20highlights%20of%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Glowtime%26quot%3B%20event%20on%20Monday.%20These%20features%20were%20first%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Worldwide%20Developers%20Conference%20(WWDC)%202024%20in%20June.%20The%20company%20is%20rolling%20them%20to%20the%20iPhone%2016%20series%20which%20was%20launched%20at%20the%20September%209%20event%2C%20as%20well%20as%20last%20year's%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20models.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fai%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-launch-apple-intelligence-ai-ios-18-1-update-features-6527298%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-gadgets360-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fai%2