ions%20and%20Features%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20and%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max%20are%20dual%20SIM%20(US%3A%20eSIM%2C%20Worldwide%3A%20Nano%2BeSIM)%20smartphones%20that%20run%20on%20iOS%2018%20out-of-the-box%20and%20are%20powered%20by%20Apple's%20second-generation%203nm%20A18%20Pro%20chip%20that%20is%20claimed%20to%20offer%20an%20XX%20increase%20in%20performance%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20models.%20Both%20phones%20will%20eventually%20offer%20support%20for%20all%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20when%20iOS%2018.1%20rolls%20out.%20Some%20of%20these%20features%20are%20currently%20unavailable%20in%20the%20EU%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20equipped%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20and%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max%20with%206.3-inch%20and%206.9-inch%20Super%20Retina%20XDR%20OLED%20displays%2C%20respectively%2C%20with%20a%20120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20(ProMotion)%2C%20up%20to%202%2C000nits%20peak%20brightness%2C%20and%C2%A0Apple's%20upgraded%20Ceramic%20Shield%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20models%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%20triple%20rear%20camera%20setup%20that%20comprises%20a%2048-megapixel%20wide%20primary%20camera%20with%20an%20f%2F1.78%20aperture%2C%20a%2012-megapixel%20ultra-wide-angle%20camera%20with%20an%20f%2F2.2%20aperture%2C%20and%20a%2012-megapixel%20telephoto%20camera%20with%20an%20f%2F2.8%20aperture%20and%20a%20'tetraprism'%20periscope%20lens%20that%20offers%20up%20to%205x%20optical%20zoom%20performance.%C2%A0A%2012-megapixel%20TrueDepth%20camera%20with%20an%20f%2F1.9%20aperture%20is%20located%20on%20the%20front%2C%20for%20taking%20video%20calls%20and%20capturing%20selfies.%20The%20phones%20also%20support%204K%20120fps%20recording.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20Action%20button%20that%20replaced%20the%20Mute%20switch%20last%20year%2C%20Apple%20has%20also%20equipped%20the%20new%20iPhone%2016%20series%20with%20a%20Capture%20button%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20quickly%20launch%20the%20camera.%C2%A0Like%20their%20predecessors%2C%20these%20phones%20have%20an%20IP68%20rating%20for%20dust%20and%20water%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20get%20up%20to%201TB%20of%20storage%20on%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20and%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max.%20The%20handsets%20offer%C2%A05G%2C%204G%20LTE%2C%20Wi-Fi%206E%2C%20Bluetooth%2C%20GPS%2C%20and%20NFC%2C%20and%20a%20USB%203.0%20Type-C%20port.%20Apple%20usually%20keeps%20battery%20capacities%20under%20wraps%2C%20but%20we%20can%20expect%20these%20details%20to%20surface%20during%20teardown%20videos%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20They%20can%20be%20charged%20at%2027W%20using%20a%20compatible%20charger%2C%20or%20at%2015W%20using%20a%20MagSafe%20or%20Qi2-compatible%20wireless%20charging%20adapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpLxyfbZE3Xg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725907200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Fiphone-16-pro-max-launch-gadgets360_1725909908027.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fmobiles%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-pro-max-price-launch-sale-date-specifications-features-6526340%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22iPhone%2016%20Pro%20and%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20Max%20were%20announced%20on%20Monday%20as%20the%20latest%20flagship%20smartphones%20at%20Apple's%20'It's%20Glowtime'%20event.%20These%20devices%20are%20the%20most%20advanced%20smartphones%20in%20the%20company's%20lineup%2C%20featuring%20the%20high-end%20A18%20Pro%20chip%2C%20which%20enables%20the%20new%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20included%20in%20iOS%2018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fmobiles%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-pro-max-price-launch-sale-date-specifications-features-6526340%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-gadgets360-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fmobiles%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-pro-max-price-launch-sale-date-specifications-features-6526340%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fmobiles%2Fnews%2Fiphone-16-pro-max-price-launch-sale-date-specifications-features-6526340%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Test%20Squad%3A%20BCCI's%20Vice-Captaincy%20Decision%20Baffles%20Everyone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20chatter%20around%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20being%20potentially%20rested%20for%20the%202-match%20Test%20series%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20marquee%20pacer%20surprisingly%20found%20a%20place%20in%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20first%20Test.%20Wicket-keeper%20batter%20Rishabh%20Pant%20also%20marked%20his%20return%20to%20the%20Test%20side%20after%20nearly%2020%20months%20out%20as%20India%20announced%20their%2016-man%20squad%20for%20the%20series%20opener%20on%20Sunday.%20While%20some%20big%20names%20returned%20to%20the%20squad%2C%20some%20prominent%20names%20missed%20out%20too.%20However%2C%20another%20decision%20from%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20selection%20committee%20that%20raised%20eyebrows%20was%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20designated%20vice-captain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20took%20on%20England%20in%20their%20last%20Test%20assignment%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20was%20named%20the%20vice-captain.%20However%2C%20no%20such%20role%20was%20allotted%20by%20the%20selection%20committee%20this%20time%2C%20making%20fans%20wonder%20what%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20is%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20in%20the%20team%2C%20alongside%20the%20likes%20of%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%20While%20Kohli%20doesn't%20want%20to%20be%20officially%20given%20a%20leadership%20role%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Pant%20are%20also%20in%20fray%20for%20India's%20long-term%20captaincy%20in%20the%20whites.%20But%2C%20none%20of%20them%20is%20a%20designated%20vice-captain%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20didn't%20explain%20the%20decision%20behind%20not%20naming%20a%20vice-captain%20either.%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20are%20expected%20to%20come%20across%20this%20question%20when%20they%20address%20press%20conference%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Test%20series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Squad%20For%20First%20Bangladesh%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20also%20made%20a%20comeback%20having%20missed%20the%20five-Test%20series%20against%20England%20at%20home%20earlier%20this%20year%20for%20having%20taken%20a%20break%20for%20the%20birth%20of%20his%20second%20child.%20While%20fast%20bowler%20Mohammed%20Shami%20remains%20on%20a%20comeback%20trail%20and%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20squad%2C%20uncapped%20left-arm%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20fast%20bowler%20Yash%20Dayal%20received%20his%20maiden%20Test%20call-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20played%20in%20the%20second%20and%20final%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh%20at%20Mirpur%20from%20December%2022-25%2C%202022%2C%20Pant%20had%20met%20a%20road%20accident%20a%20few%20days%20later%20on%20December%2030%20and%20made%20his%20return%20to%20top%20flight%20cricket%20only%20in%20IPL%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20Test%20side%20even%20though%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20had%20earlier%20expressed%20that%20the%20right-arm%20seamer%20was%20targeting%20a%20return%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDayal%2C%20who%20was%20once%20smashed%20for%20five%20consecutive%20sixes%20by%20Rinku%20Singh%20in%20an%20IPL%20match%2C%20has%20had%20a%20remarkable%20redemption%20with%20his%20India%20call-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20Rahul%2C%20who%20suffered%20a%20right%20quadriceps%20injury%20after%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20England%20at%20Hyderabad%2C%20also%20returned%20to%20the%20Test%20side.%20He%20