Bjust%20steady%20improvements%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Techsponential%20analyst%20Avi%20Greengart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELonger%20term%2C%20Apple%20could%20dramatically%20change%20the%20iPhone%20experience%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper-powered%20Siri%26quot%3B%20working%20across%20all%20the%20apps%2C%20Greengart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPixel%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20announcement%20closely%20follows%20Google%2C%20which%20last%20month%20unveiled%20AI-infused%20Pixel%209%20smartphones%2C%20its%20challenge%20to%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPixels%20account%20for%20a%20tiny%20sliver%20of%20the%20global%20smartphone%20market%20dominated%20by%20Samsung%20and%20Apple%2C%20but%20Google%20argued%20its%20new%20line%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20answer%20what%20--%20after%20all%20the%20hype%20--%20AI%20can%20actually%20do%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20so%20many%20promises%2C%20so%20many%20'coming%20soons%2C'%20and%20not%20enough%20real%20world%20helpfulness%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%20--%20which%20is%20why%20today%20we're%20getting%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20devices%20Rick%20Osterloh%20said%20at%20the%20Pixel%209%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamsung%20has%20also%20showcased%20AI%20across%20a%20range%20of%20its%20consumer%20electronic%20products%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20extend%20its%20leadership%20in%20global%20smartphone%20sales.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725906900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F13dof9ho_iphone-16-pro_625x300_09_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-iphone-16-launch-live-apple-unveils-new-iphone-built-for-artificial-i