E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fapple-iphone-16-plus-price-in-india-128235%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20launched%20by%20Apple%20on%20Monday%20at%20its%20latest%20hardware%20launch%20event.%20These%20smartphones%20are%20powered%20by%20a%20new%20A18%20chip%20and%20run%20on%20iOS%2018%2C%20along%20with%20support%20for%20Apple%20Intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company's%20take%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI).%20Like%20their%20predecessors%2C%20they%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%20dual%20rear%20camera%20setup.%20The%20iPhone%2016%20and%20iPhone%2016%20Plus%20also%20feature%20the%20Action%20button%20that%20arrived%20with%20the%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20models%20last%20year%2C%20and%20a%20new%20Camera%20Control%20button.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EiPhone%2016%2C%20iPhone%2016%20Plus%20Pricing%20and%20Availability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EiPhone%2016%20pricing%20starts%20at%20%24799%20(roughly%20Rs.%2067%2C100)%2C%20while%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Plus%20starts%20at%20%24899%20(roughly%20Rs.%2075%2C500)%20for%20the%20base%20128GB%20variant.%20Both%20phones%20are%20available%20with%20up%20to%20512GB%20of%20storage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EiPhone%2016%2C%20iPhone%2016%20Plus%20specifications%20and%20features%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20launched%20iPhone%2016%20is%20a%20dual%20SIM%20(US%3A%20eSIM%2C%20Worldwide%3A%20Nano%2BeSIM)%20handset%20that%20runs%20on%20iOS%2018.%20It%20is%20powered%20by%20a%203nm%20octa-core%20A18%20chipset%20that%20features%20a%206-core%20CPU%2C%205-core%20GPU%2C%20and%20a%2016-core%20neural%20engine.%20Like%20the%20iPhone%2016%20Pro%20model%2C%20these%20phones%20will%20support%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20showcased%20by%20the%20company%20at%20WWDC%202024%20that%20will%20also%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20equipped%20the%20iPhone%2016%20with%20a%C2%A06.1-inch%20Super%20Retina%20XDR%20OLED%20display%20with%20up%20to%202%2C000%20