22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fblack-powder-how-female-genitalia-is-mutilated-for-magic-love-potions-in-this-african-nation%2Famp_articleshow%2F113196580.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20People%20Accept%20Me%2C%20Fine%26quot%3B%3A%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20Daughter%20On%20Poll%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bijbehara%20constituency%20of%20Anantnag%20has%20been%20a%20bastion%20of%20Mufti%20family%20since%201990s.%20The%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20-%20formed%20by%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20father%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mufti%20Mohammed%20Sayeed%20--%20has%20been%20winning%20from%20this%20seat%20since%201996.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20third%20generation%20of%20the%20Mufti%20family%20-%20Mufti's%20grand-daughter%20Iltija%20Mufti%20-%20is%20making%20her%20electoral%20debut%20from%20this%20constituency%20after%20her%20mother%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20declined%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20has%20said%20that%20she%20would%20not%20contest%20as%20long%20as%20J%26amp%3BK%20remains%20a%20Union%20Territory%20and%20its%20special%20status%20is%20not%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20on%20September%2018%20will%20be%20three-cornered%2C%20but%20the%20main%20fight%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20between%20Iltija%20Mufti%20and%20National%20Conference's%20Dr%20Bashir%20Veeri.%20The%20third%20candidate%20is%20BJPs%20Sufi%20Yousf.%20The%20number%20of%20candidates%20here%20is%20the%20lowest%20of%20any%20constituency%20in%20Kashmir.%20No%20Independent%20is%20in%20fray%2C%20even%20though%2044%20per%20cent%20of%20candidates%20contesting%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20phase%20of%20elections%20are%20Independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIltija%20Mufti%20appears%20both%20confident%20and%20cautious%20about%20her%20election%20prospects%20as%20she%20flits%20between%20villages%20nestled%20amid%20apple%20orchards%20and%20gushing%20streams.%20The%2037-year-old%20is%20trying%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20legacy%20of%20her%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPropaganda%20against%20dynastic%20politics%20doesn't%20bother%20her%2C%20she%20said%2C%20because%20it%20is%20she%20who%20will%20be%20accepted%20or%20rejected%20by%20people%20during%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20people%20accept%20me%2C%20fine.%20If%20they%20don't%2C%20not%20a%20big%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20a%20subtle%20hint%20of%20what%20she%20thought%20of%20the%20contest%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20complacent%20about%20elections...%20even%20if%20it%20is%20easy%20I%20don't%20take%20it%20easy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mufti's%20main%20rival%20is%20Dr%20Bashir%20Ahmad%20Veeri%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20candidate.%20A%20former%20legislator%2C%20Dr%20Veeri%20talks%20about%20local%20and%20livelihood%20issues%20along%20with%20his%20party's%20larger%20political%20narrative.%20The%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20how%20it%20has%20impacted%20the%20people%20and%20their%20identity%20is%20central%20to%20the%20campaign%20of%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIltija%20mufti's%20candidates%20doesn't%20make%20any%20difference%20to%20him%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20there%20was%20a%20PDP%20wave%2C%20because%20they%20had%20set%20a%20narrative%20that%20if%20you%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20BJP%2C%20vote%20for%20PDP...%20this%20time%20it's%20very%20favourable%20scenario%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP's%20subsequent%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20had%20collapsed%20in%202018%20as%20the%20BJP%20ended%20ties.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20the%20BJP%20scrapped%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20granted%20under%20the%20Constitution's%20Article%20370%20and%20split%20the%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories.%20This%20year's%20election%20will%20be%20the%20first%20after%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20claims%20credit%20for%20helping%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20turn%20over%20a%20new%20leaf%20-%20a%20positive%20one%20where%20the%20diktat%20of%20terrorists%20does%20not%20matter%20--%20said%20the%20people%20are%20quietly%20supporting%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESofi%20Yousf%20said%20the%20people%20are%20supporting%20him%20as%20they%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20bringing%20peace%20in%20the%20Valley.%20The%20biggest%20mark%20of%20that%20change%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20has%20joined%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20regional%20party%20leaders%20have%20nothing%20to%20offer%20to%20people.%20They%20are%20only%20spreading%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20promise%20to%20people%20is%20development...%20these%20people%20have%20known%20me%20for%20last%2025%20years.%20I%20have%20been%20helping%20them...%20I%20promise%20the%20people%20Bijbehara%20that%20all%20those%20in%20jails%20will%20be%20released%20the%20way%20Rajnath%20Singh%20as%20Home%20Minister%20withdrew%2012%2C000%20cases%20against%20the%20young%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725896580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fhvsid04_iltija-mufti_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-people-accept-me-fine-mehbooba-muftis-daughter-on-poll-debut-6527486%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bijbehara%20constituency%20of%20Anantnag%20has%20been%20a%20bastion%20of%20Mufti%20family%20since%201990s.%20The%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20-%20formed%20by%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20father%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mufti%20Mohammed%20Sayeed%20--%20has%20been%20winning%20from%20this%20seat%20since%201996.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C