%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiren%20Rijiju%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20also%20said%20that%20overlapping%20of%20patrolling%20by%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20forces%20does%20take%20place%20in%20the%20undemarcated%20areas%20along%20the%20Sino-Indian%20border%20but%20that%20does%20not%20lead%20to%20encroachment%20of%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20minister's%20comments%20came%20amidst%20reports%20that%20the%20PLA%20allegedly%20entered%20inside%20Indian%20territory%20in%20the%20Anjaw%20district%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20last%20week%20and%20they%20were%20camping%20in%20the%20Kapapu%20area%20of%20the%20district%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPictures%20of%20bonfires%2C%20painting%20of%20rocks%20and%20Chinese%20food%20materials%20found%20at%20the%20site%20have%20been%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20can't%20take%20our%20land.%20Overlapping%20of%20patrolling%20does%20take%20place%20in%20the%20undemarcated%20areas.%20They%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20construct%20anything%20permanent.%20There%20is%20strict%20vigil%20from%20our%20side.%20Mere%20painting%20of%20marks%20in%20undemarcated%20locations%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20areas%20have%20been%20encroached%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20told%20PTI%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20minister%20said%20India%20has%20been%20building%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20border%20and%20that%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20come%20near%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20incident%20came%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Indian%20army%20continues%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20stand-off%20with%20the%20PLA%20in%20Ladakh.%20The%20stand-off%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%20April%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20shares%20a%203%2C400%20km-long%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20with%20China%20from