er%20over%20several%20years%20to%20maintain%20his%20job%20security.%20He%20claimed%20that%20Alvarado-Gil%20had%20a%20proclivity%20for%20oral%20sex%20and%20that%20she%20treated%20it%20as%20a%20perk%20of%20power.%20He%20is%20now%20seeking%20monetary%20damages%20for%20the%20allegations%20including%20lost%20wages%2C%20loss%20of%20earning%20capacity%2C%20employee%20benefits%20and%20damages%20for%20emotional%20distress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F766673247%2FMarie-Alvarado-Gil-Lawsuit%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20filed%20in%20the%20Sacramento%20County%20Superior%20Court%2C%20claims%20that%20for%20much%20of%202023%2C%20state%20Senator%20Marie%20Alvarado-Gil%20(R-Jackson)%20''engaged%20in%20erratic%2C%20controlling%2C%20sexually%20dominating%20abuse%20of%20authority%20and%20power''%20against%20her%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Chad%20Condit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20alleges%20that%20the%20Senator%20frequently%20demanded%20oral%20sex%20from%20her%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20including%20in%20a%20vehicle%2C%20one%20of%20which%20led%20to%20a%20back%20injury.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Mr%20Condit%20claimed%20he%20suffered%20three%20herniated%20discs%20in%20his%20back%20and%20a%20collapsed%20hip.%20He%20revealed%20that%20he%C2%A0began%20using%20his%20back%20injury%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20decline%20the%20Senator's%20advances%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20she%20responded%20by%20issuing%20a%20disciplinary%20letter%20accusing%20him%20of%20inappropriate%20behaviour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20was%20a%20sex-based%20quid%20pro%20quo%20relationship%20of%20unwelcome%20advances%20and%20sexual%20behaviours%20coupled%20with%20punishment%20and%20flexing%20of%20power%2C''%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Alvarado-Gil%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20in%202022%2C%20hired%20Chad%20Condit%20as%20her%20chief%20of%20staff.%20The%20lawsuit%20claims%20that%20shortly%20after%20taking%20office%2C%20the%20Senator%20began%20sharing%20personal%20and%20intimate%20details%20with%20him%2C%20including%20aspects%20of%20her%20dating%20life%2C%20divorces%2C%20and%20marital%20infidelity.%20According%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20she%20also%20openly%20discussed%20her%20struggles%20and%20habits%2C%20including%20substance%20use%20and%20recreational%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20terminated%20his%20employment%20in%20December%202023%20after%20he%20refused%C2%A0to%20wear%20a%20Santa%20Claus%20costume%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20was%20not%20required%20of%20other%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20Alvarado-Gil%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20calling%20the%20claims%20''bogus''%20and%20''financially%20motivated.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''A%20disgruntled%20former%20employee%20has%20fabricated%20an%20outlandish%20story%2C%20presented%20without%20evidence%2C%20to%20get%20a%20payday.%20We%20expect%20that%20the%20Senator%20will%20be%20fully%20cleared%20of%20any%20wrongdoing%20of%20these%20bogus%2C%20financially%20motivated%20claims%2C''%20attorney%20Ognian%20Gavrilov%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Senator%20also%20recently%20made%20headlines%20when%20she%20switched%20parties%20from%20Democrat%20to%20Republican%2C%20citing%20concerns%20that%20her%20former%20party's%20leadership%20and%20policies%20had%20changed%20in%20ways%20that%20no%20longer%20aligned%20with%20her%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlvardo-Gil%20is%20married%20and%20has%20six%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725896100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F176btfj8_marie-alvaradogil_625x300_09_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcalifornia-state-senator-used-her-male-chief-of-staff-as-sex-slave-claims-lawsuit-6526899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20Chad%20Condit%2C%20claims%20that%20he%20was%20subjected%20to%2