0Rs%2012%2C000%20to%20Rs%2014%2C000%20every%20month.%20It%20can%20also%20increase%20depending%20on%20factors%20like%20sales%20and%20special%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20these%20women%2C%20Iris%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfghan%20women%20have%20a%20pleasant%20demeanour.%20They%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20their%20heritage.%20They%20listen%20to%20my%20instructions%20and%20are%20not%20afraid%20to%20disagree%20with%20me%20when%20necessary.%20They%20have%20shown%20amazing%20resilience%20in%20rebuilding%20their%20lives%20in%20India%2C%20however%20temporary%20their%20current%20residence%20may%20be.%20Many%20SilaiWali%20women%20have%20broken%20the%20glass%20ceiling%20by%20being%20the%20sole-earning%20members%20of%20their%20families.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20these%20families%20were%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Their%20children%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20sent%20to%20school.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20our%20intervention%20has%20somewhat%20eased%20their%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Iris%2C%20who%20finds%20this%20work%20extremely%20fulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20journalism%20to%20establish%20a%20career%20in%20the%20social%20enterprise%20sector%2C%20Bishwadeep%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20do%20impacts%20so%20many%20families%20and%20provides%20them%20with%20dignity%2C%20spending%20power%2C%20demolishing%20the%20patriarchal%20system%2C%20and%20creating%20an%20impact%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20work%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20directly%20engage%20with%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20at%20the%20grassroots.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20SilaiWali%20social%20verticals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725030423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-1-1